snippet.title: Cooking Companions Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1263230/Cooking_Companions/


Cooking Companions will release on October 7th, 2021 right after the Steam Next Fest concludes! Look forward to an updated demo with plenty of surprises.
